{"tid":1850053,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(正式上線) 抗疫物品配對平台 - 全城齊抗疫 兄弟姊妹一個都不能少","createTime":"2020-01-29T10:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T06:20:16.000Z","uid":2478,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e68e5244c7c98db180a96227d896eea0a7344839","tid":1850053,"uid":2478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:50:57.000Z","msg":"有鑒於政府無能穩定抗疫物品供應，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟整咗個抗疫物品配對表格，等有充餘物資的手足可以有效地幫助另一位手足<br />\n<br />\n表格內接受多種抗疫物品去做配對<br />\n包括: 口罩、消毒酒精、搓手液、消毒濕紙巾、消毒藥水、漂白水<br />\n你可以選擇以無償方式捐出，亦可以填寫目標價格 (炒賣死全家)<br />\n<br />\n表格亦都允許你選擇所提供的物品指定比特定人員<br />\n(包括: 社福界、教育界、醫護界、高風險職工、家庭 等等)<br />\n<br />\n配對成功後，結果會以電郵通知「提供者」及「需求者」<br />\n皆時雙方可以私下聯絡交收事宜<br />\n免卻遭暴力藍絲圍堵 或 遭訊息轟炸<br />\n<br />\n若果係需要抗疫物品，就填呢個表格:<a href=\"https://forms.gle/HRmVfLutqR27eAiH7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FHRmVfLutqR27eAiH7&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH9AAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=b9ca80c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/HRmVfLutqR27eAiH7</a><br />\n若果係提供抗疫物品，就填呢個表格:<a href=\"https://forms.gle/KpR8Nt8JqHwWNiey5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FKpR8Nt8JqHwWNiey5&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH9AAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=7db7ded9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/KpR8Nt8JqHwWNiey5</a><br />\n<br />\n若果你係預覽Post已經填過就無須再填<br />\n<br />\n政府唔做，我地做!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府做，我地做得更好更有效率!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n若各位有咩建議或改善地方，請各位留言，我會盡力改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現時配對係得人手處理，可能會比較慢，請大家見諒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都會更新現時需求情況，等大家知道。<br />\n即使大家無咩需要用到呢個服務，都請推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全城齊抗疫 兄弟姊妹一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062fd2e7d3e67a4c87405760cbd8345a642157e1","tid":1850053,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:00:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Spin 咗嚟抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ead389a06975d3fe7689af9c197b0882b9b99db7","tid":1850053,"uid":2478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"620e95b7830bfdae70b17932ce7e59db12faeca5","tid":1850053,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:46:13.000Z","msg":"以物易物tg group 算啦"},{"pid":"61a7c1691104751bcb5a1b2621a9641187bfd9ac","tid":1850053,"uid":2478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa649cba32a95a5adb818d30b8dc87e5b3df9102","tid":1850053,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"雙氧水，洗甲水，甲醇可以代替消毒火酒嗎？"},{"pid":"d8b278c08a376bfa5bfeac64193c9d2623d738e2","tid":1850053,"uid":2478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa649cba32a95a5adb818d30b8dc87e5b3df9102","tid":1850053,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"雙氧水，洗甲水，甲醇可以代替消毒火酒嗎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:31:32.000Z","msg":"三樣都唔得<br />\n甲醇直頭有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ebc8a2eb806b8a3f6184a45a80000890bd20d41","tid":1850053,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8b278c08a376bfa5bfeac64193c9d2623d738e2","tid":1850053,"uid":2478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa649cba32a95a5adb818d30b8dc87e5b3df9102","tid":1850053,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy